text: Ceroplesis elgonensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1923 and is known from Kenya.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis elgonensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesis Category:Beetles described in 1923
